{"tid":923003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【扼殺童真】「聖誕老人不是真的！」 老師一句話搞到學校要道歉","createTime":"2018-12-01T01:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T09:13:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c31eccf1a41a76230cff2d9ac96e647397cba1cb","tid":923003,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"美國新澤西州一名代課老師，令一班小學一年級學生童心破碎。她周四在課堂上告訴這些只有幾歲的小孩：聖誕老人不是真的！<br />\n該位在蒙特維爾(Montville)Cedar Hill小學代課的老師，一句說話把孩童對聖誕節的幻想戮破，累得學校當局慌忙向家長致函道歉。<br />\n該校一位高層雷茲(Michael Raj)在信上說：「作為一名4歲孩子的父親，我深深了解該番說話是如何敏感。」他表示有責任告知家長該名老師的「愚笨」行為，讓他們有所準備，一旦孩子未來數天問起聖誕老人的問題，他們也可適當應對，在聖誕佳節下保留孩童一份純真。<br />\n雷茲表示已訓斥該位代課老師，指她判斷能力差劣。該校校監對此事也深感困擾和沮喪。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181201/large/1543621116_b822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181201%2Flarge%2F1543621116_b822.jpg&h=143185c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181201/58979211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979211&d=1puHGPAGbSmSENI0cD9hRjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0e3b2a9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181201%2F58979211&h=242887dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181201/58979211</a>"},{"pid":"f01c379f166d8156e4da760564ce6b9fdf10ece9","tid":923003,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:18:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d044b11d37b0eae8080017b62d62e831cc582824","tid":923003,"uid":39974,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"講真話都係罪"},{"pid":"4ba6a182875a53448ad43a0cd5c180d62c632524","tid":923003,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f01c3